       Foster City, CA, USA, 6–10 October 2014; ACM Press: New York, NY,
       USA, 2014; pp. 285–288. [Google Scholar] [CrossRef]
   42. Vargas, S.; Castells, P. Rank and relevance in novelty and
       diversity metrics for recommender systems. In Proceedings of the
       Fifth ACM Conference on Recommender Systems, Chicago, IL, USA,
       23–27 October 2011; ACM Press: New York, NY, USA, 2011; pp.
       109–116. [Google Scholar] [CrossRef]
   43. De Gemmis, M.; Lops, P.; Semeraro, G.; Musto, C. An investigation
       on the serendipity problem in recommender systems. Inf. Process.
